snippet.title: Gutchan Bank (ぐっちゃんばんく) for the NEC PC-88
snippet.description:
Came also out for:

FM-7


Game description:

In Gutchan Bank you play as either Gutchan or his girlfriend Marichan.
You have to collect the coins and money bags, as well as ID cards.
The enemies that run around will steal them. All of the enemies have different patterns and some might even stun the player.
There are bags with a question mark on it. Those contain items with which the player can overcome one enemy.
